  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bb2\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bca\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0b87\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0b9e\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A young man who took part in an anti-government protest was killed",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "A young man who took part in the anti-government protest in front of the Prime Minister's office has died.",
        "Jaliya Dissanayake (26 years old), a father of a child from Thaladagama area of \u200b\u200bKurunegala, who participated in today's protest, has lost his life.",
        "It has been revealed from the investigations that the youth who was the target of teargas attack while participating in the protest died of respiratory failure."
      ],
